HEADWORD: Lamantin
<hw>La*man"tin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>lamantin</ets>, <ets>lamentin</ets>, prob. from the name of the
animal in the Antilles. Cf. <er>Manater</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The manatee.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>lamentin</asp>, and
<asp>lamantine</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

